text:
Simple street side stall selling home made muah chee. First time seeing this stall located right at the cross street in front of bierhaus.

It’s been sold by a foreign lady as she don’t really understand when I was speaking with her. Probably someone hire her to sell there. Anywhere the muah chee was soft and the peanuts generous. One packet for 5 ringgit seems reasonable.

Tiz review Is meant for their stall in Permas Jaya on Sunday. Used to be managed by chinese owner. But now leave to foreign lady worker to manage. Hygience is an issue. On 1 Sept 2024, I saw her touching her bare foot while waiting customer. and later served Customer without washing hand, not wearing glove. So disgusting.
Their muah Chee is warmy and soft with peanut coating is so satisfying.
